{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"712da7f411","title":"纠正军队生产偏向是为至要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a237844029","index":0,"year":1950,"month":4,"day":2,"articleId":"712da7f411"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"9fba1d952b","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"712da7f411","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会起草的转发中国人民解放军华北军区1950年3月31日关于纠正军队生产偏向指示的电报。"},{"id":"b4460be085","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"712da7f411","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指示电中提出应当纠正的军队生产中出现的偏向是：（一）集中力量搞生产，放松了汇任务；（二）工具未准备好，劳动量过度；（三）管理松解，引起战士逃亡；（四）生产动员时片面强调分红，对增加国家财富和减轻人民负担的精神强调不够。"}],"contents":[{"id":"5a9e65eab6","type":"title","text":"纠正军队生产偏向是为至要","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"712da7f411"},{"id":"9fba1d952b","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局、各军区：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"712da7f411"},{"id":"b4460be085","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将华北军区三月册一日关于纠正军队生产偏向指示电一件发给你们，望转发所属参考并纠正自己部队中的偏向，是为至要","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"712da7f411"},{"id":"f517ccaa78","type":"paragraph","text":"中央军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"712da7f411"},{"id":"041933e59e","type":"paragraph","text":"四月二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"712da7f411"}],"page":{"id":"b51daba087","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"712da7f411","start":254,"end":254}}}},"__N_SSG":true}